.TH il-verify 1 "Zanna" "zanna-il-verify" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
il-verify \- Verify a Zanna IL module for structural correctness
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B il-verify
\fIFILE.il\fR
.br
.B il-verify
\fB--version\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
Parses a textual IL module and runs the structural verifier, reporting diagnostics to stderr. Prints \fCOK\fR on success.
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success; 1 on argument, I/O, parse, or verification failure.
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBzanna\fR(1), \fBilrun\fR(1)

